CHAPTER VI
FUNDS
Conditions on investment. . ( ) In order to make an investment in an alternative investment fund or a mutual fund operating
in IFSC, the investor shall be: (i) a person resident outside India;
(ii) a non-resident Indian;
(iii) institutional investor resident in India who is eligible under FEMA to invest funds
